{"tid":60367,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊家居裝修 , 你問我盡量答","createTime":"2016-12-30T11:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-04T03:27:38.000Z","uid":71141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c743f876b49def8b613727c9127da942efd741e0","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"頭先係隔黎大陸訂傢俬中伏個POST到見到<br />\n好多人唔係好清楚裝修係點既一回事<br />\n所以想開個POST同大家分享下<br />\n小弟識唔晒咁多工種<br />\n不過都盡量回答你地既問題啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n問 : 點解新砌個幅牆同天花夾位,新砌個陣無事,但住左1,2年就有裂紋?<br />\n<br />\n首先天花同磚牆既物料同密度唔同 <br />\n天花係石屎而牆身係沙/紅磚加英泥沙再批灰油油<br />\n新砌既牆經過一年四季之後會有冷縮熱漲既現象<br />\n而天花之前已經經過左之後就會無咁多收縮<br />\n所以9成9都會出現裂紋,多數都唔關做野個師傅事<br />\n<br />\n解決方法 :<br />\n等牆身收縮定左,叫師傅/自己係裂紋到補滿灰,<br />\n灰乾左就用沙紙省平,之後而用油掃油返油就OK<br />\n<br />\n問2 : 買左衣櫃貼埋牆但係有個V字既縫隙,個櫃唔直?<br />\n<br />\n首先牆身同地台面,基本上無可能100%平/直,只會視角上係直角<br />\n而衣櫃係大陸訂/香港訂(多數都係大陸廠做)<br />\n都好少會因為個櫃唔夠直身而出現V縫<br />\n建議買把平水尺(平D)/其他平水儀器CHECK下係咪關個櫃事先<br />\n<br />\n解決方法 :<br />\n隔黎POST都有巴打解答左 去五金鋪買支白色填縫膠<br />\n加滿之後再剷平,就會望落順眼好多 (睇唔明就搵師傅整啦)"},{"pid":"7f2128daf010151ed3a75d2fcdaa01a1816ed509","tid":60367,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"搭棚佬留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f223d1ef985b0a418d8c3b244f24b1c8378732d","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"即管問 我盡量答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e887088fac17c904ac49b7f563113c9e542b00","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"仲以為會有好多人問野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a19f306f4ce168879334934d88dfb131b0da5b","tid":60367,"uid":6946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"邊個工種最貴/最平"},{"pid":"e9789e388a571cc3a9eed521874b6e5dd18736c0","tid":60367,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"請唔請人 21歲"},{"pid":"9a37597ba607a5153a81981c613b7459221718f6","tid":60367,"uid":64602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"builder 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4de3bc21431a15327db5ad676a781dd707d5bb","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個工種最貴/最平</blockquote><br />\n泥水佬應該最貴,因為有技術加勁辛苦<br />\n油漆同水電,算搵少D不過都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c65611372130307b4be29bdef39b5dfbf977db","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請唔請人 21歲</blockquote><br />\n未有本事請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e71bdc29bf5637b10eb8f94bf64ccb334a61df","tid":60367,"uid":63631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3a54bf1de876865b120c663f16e5a57df5257b0d","tid":60367,"uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"乜月份你地最忙？如果過年前完，要預早幾多揾你地？"},{"pid":"80a28f8aeed3084e443d52c0b1945f4a47a2f826","tid":60367,"uid":63127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"有冇一d 野係室內設計師提出完而你地做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff00784c497da2983f442dc5f5c57cf1c6d51d8","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜月份你地最忙？如果過年前完，要預早幾多揾你地？</blockquote><br />\n一般全屋大搞從清場到交貨3個月內左右<br />\n有行家2個月交到,又有聽過有人半年都未交到貨比個客<br />\n預幾耐就要睇你搵個師傅忙唔忙,佢有時間既你今日搵佢,後日可以開工"},{"pid":"8f5872b8d2b1e5ba9cf7179dd42e28760fa010f3","tid":60367,"uid":64602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊個工種最貴/最平</blockquote><br />\n泥水佬應該最貴,因為有技術加勁辛苦<br />\n油漆同水電,算搵少D不過都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真，不過好多泥水佬功夫真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd01b39ebee51a9352570f7441ff9fd409efa9d","tid":60367,"uid":13433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"想買個漫畫櫃 邊度先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出去睇 度度都係書櫃 冇漫畫size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef19cb39495dbbaa31305c2e913bdad30ea87f5a","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇一d 野係室內設計師提出完而你地做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己角度係得好少野做唔到<br />\n但係多數野都係同錢掛鉤,肯比錢咪有囉,比唔夠錢咪做唔到囉"},{"pid":"122b95fdf02c92ab9f896530b956c1a247e52819","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想買個漫畫櫃 邊度先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出去睇 度度都係書櫃 冇漫畫size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔高要求既去IKEA搵下<br />\n想FIT SIZE去傢俬鋪訂造(唔平)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e791367b5f9a3a4e531000e4b12e02d02589f5f0","tid":60367,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"人工如何 想入行"},{"pid":"4e0e8c75e299ba84cdee5cacc8d704780f0117f3","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工如何 想入行</blockquote><br />\n師傅最少都1200+/1工<br />\n少人入行 應該會越黎越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0573cec42357d0b844d01e873669596e06ff340","tid":60367,"uid":13433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人工如何 想入行</blockquote><br />\n師傅最少都1200+/1工<br />\n少人入行 應該會越黎越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早兩年白紙一張做泥水 得350 蚊包餐飯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b1a074c2a29e1891133c888f6fe847bb80c9f9","tid":60367,"uid":59226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"有咩最快方法去甲醛?<br />\n驚唔驚吸得太多生癌?"},{"pid":"6f6fd146f0028fb8c3a95f839dc36a516a1f6814","tid":60367,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"1 有冇搞過日式鋪頭裝修<br />\n2 係你地畫埋圖定係個客搵公司畫哂照做<br />\n3 報價既標準係點報"},{"pid":"bf9d68fc706cf7ec86f9490d5b6d0b9dd0934a34","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人工如何 想入行</blockquote><br />\n師傅最少都1200+/1工<br />\n少人入行 應該會越黎越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早兩年白紙一張做泥水 得350 蚊包餐飯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過度期黎姐 到你學有所成 月入4-50k不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7aeaeb16ac6f3a4e7ec3f8c98fe9ee82720896b","tid":60367,"uid":71141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1 有冇搞過日式鋪頭裝修<br />\n2 係你地畫埋圖定係個客搵公司畫哂照做<br />\n3 報價既標準係點報</blockquote><br />\n1 無 <br />\n2 一般你搵既室內設計公司會度尺畫圖之後同你傾內容同報價比你,通常都包埋設計同裝修費<br />\n但都可以自己畫張示意圖/上網見到既相,同設計師商量點做<br />\n3 報價係計要整幾多野,同咩物料,設計費(如果有)加要賺你既錢=總數<br />\n無咩標準,睇你搵咩公司做"},{"pid":"4b690ecda19dbb182583e42077c2f81dcdae5b84","tid":60367,"uid":343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"樓主自己接嚟做？搵幾錢個月平均<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}